parameters.text:
=Analyze the following hotel guest feedback and provide a comprehensive sentiment analysis:

Guest Name: {{ $json.guestName }}
Room Number: {{ $json.roomNumber }}
Overall Rating: {{ $json.overallRating }}/5
Service Area: {{ $json.serviceArea }}
Feedback: {{ $json.feedbackText }}

Provide your analysis in the following JSON format:
{
  "sentiment": "positive/neutral/negative",
  "sentimentScore": 0-100,
  "urgencyLevel": "low/medium/high/critical",
  "keyIssues": ["issue1", "issue2"],
  "emotionalTone": "description",
  "requiresImmediateAction": true/false,
  "suggestedRecoveryAction": "specific recommendation",
  "estimatedImpactOnReputation": "low/medium/high",
  "categories": ["cleanliness", "staff", "amenities", etc.],
  "summary": "brief summary of the feedback"
}
